1265.name: FL 838
1265.Applications: Vessels, tanks, boilers, steam turbines, shafts, valves, cladding steel rollers with stainless steel and Nickel based alloys
1265.Suitable_For: FL 838 can be used for a weight range of wire types such as: stainless steel, and nickel based wires ranging from :308L, 316L, 347, 317L, Duplex 2209, Super Duplex 2507 and 2594, 1.4410,  9% Nickel steels and practically all other simmilar grades.
